---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="This Week in Global Investing - Get Global Yields">
  <section class="w-full px-4 pt-10 pb-14 sm:px-6 sm:pt-12 sm:pb-16 lg:px-8 lg:pt-14 lg:pb-20">
    <div class="weekly-update-container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="icon-circle">
          <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 11.25v7.5m-9-6h.008v.008H12v-.008zM12 15h.008v.008H12V15zm0 2.25h.008v.008H12v-.008zM9.75 15h.008v.008H9.75V15zm0 2.25h.008v.008H9.75v-.008zM7.5 15h.008v.008H7.5V15zm0 2.25h.008v.008H7.5v-.008zm6.75-4.5h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 2.25h.008v.008h-.008V15zm0 2.25h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm2.25-4.5h.008v.008H16.5v-.008zm0 2.25h.008v.008H16.5V15z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1>This Week in <span>Global Investing</span></h1>
        <p>Curated updates for international investors - regulations, brokers, taxes, and key stats.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="update-banner" id="update-banner">
        <span class="pulse-dot"></span>
        Content updated manually each week - last updated: <strong id="last-updated-date">June 9, 2026</strong>
      </div>

      <div class="cards-grid" id="cards-grid">
        <div class="card regulatory" data-card="regulatory">
          <div class="card-accent-bar"></div>
          <span class="category-badge">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126zM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008z" /></svg>
            Market Update
          </span>
          <div class="headline" data-field="headline">International Stocks Outperform US 4:1 in 2026</div>
          <div class="summary" data-field="summary">Bank of America reports $104 billion flowed into international stocks in 2026 versus only $25 billion into US stocks. The S&P 500 is up just 0.5% YTD while the Vanguard Total International ETF is up 11%.</div>
          <div class="date-tag" data-field="week">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 11.25v7.5" /></svg>
            Week of June 9, 2026
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card broker" data-card="broker">
          <div class="card-accent-bar"></div>
          <span class="category-badge">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 7.5L7.5 3m0 0L12 7.5M7.5 3v13.5m13.5 0L16.5 21m0 0L12 16.5m4.5 4.5V7.5" /></svg>
            Broker News
          </span>
          <div class="headline" data-field="headline">IBKR Launches AI Trading via Claude Integration</div>
          <div class="summary" data-field="summary">Interactive Brokers launched agentic trading through Claude AI, allowing clients to manage accounts and execute trades across 170+ global markets using natural language. International investors can now use conversational AI to interact with their IBKR account directly.</div>
          <div class="date-tag" data-field="week">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 11.25v7.5" /></svg>
            Week of June 9, 2026
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card tax" data-card="tax">
          <div class="card-accent-bar"></div>
          <span class="category-badge">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" /></svg>
            Broker News
          </span>
          <div class="headline" data-field="headline">IBKR Offers International Clients Access to SpaceX IPO</div>
          <div class="summary" data-field="summary">Interactive Brokers UK is giving eligible clients access to the SpaceX IPO on Nasdaq. A rare example of a major IPO accessible to international investors through their broker account.</div>
          <div class="date-tag" data-field="week">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 11.25v7.5" /></svg>
            Week of June 9, 2026
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card stat" data-card="stat">
          <div class="card-accent-bar"></div>
          <span class="category-badge">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z" /></svg>
            Stat of the Week
          </span>
          <div class="headline" data-field="headline">IBKR Records 4.97 Million Daily Trades in May 2026</div>
          <div class="summary" data-field="summary">Interactive Brokers reported 4.969 million DARTs in May 2026, reflecting continued growth in global retail trading. IBKR remains the most active broker for international investors by trading volume.</div>
          <div class="date-tag" data-field="week">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 11.25v7.5" /></svg>
            Week of June 9, 2026
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="admin-hint">Press Ctrl+Shift+E to open admin editor</div>

      <div class="admin-panel" id="admin-panel">
        <h2>
          <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.862 4.487l1.687-1.688a1.875 1.875 0 112.652 2.652L10.582 16.07a4.5 4.5 0 01-1.897 1.13L6 18l.8-2.685a4.5 4.5 0 011.13-1.897l8.932-8.931zm0 0L19.5 7.125M18 14v4.75A2.25 2.25 0 0115.75 21H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 013 18.75V8.25A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 6H10" /></svg>
          Admin Editor
        </h2>
        <p class="admin-subtitle">Edit each card below, then click "Apply Changes" to update the live preview. Use "Copy HTML" to export the section.</p>

        <div id="admin-cards-container"></div>

        <div class="admin-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-apply" id="btn-apply">Apply Changes</button>
          <button class="btn btn-copy" id="btn-copy">Copy Updated HTML</button>
          <span class="copy-feedback" id="copy-feedback">Copied!</span>
          <button class="btn btn-close" id="btn-close-admin">Close Editor</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="disclaimer">
        <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> The information in this section is for educational and informational purposes only. Regulatory and tax information changes frequently - always verify with official sources or a qualified professional before making decisions.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script is:inline>
    (function() {
      const adminPanel = document.getElementById('admin-panel');
      const adminCardsContainer = document.getElementById('admin-cards-container');
      const cardsGrid = document.getElementById('cards-grid');
      const updateBanner = document.getElementById('update-banner');
      const lastUpdatedDate = document.getElementById('last-updated-date');
      const btnApply = document.getElementById('btn-apply');
      const btnCopy = document.getElementById('btn-copy');
      const btnClose = document.getElementById('btn-close-admin');
      const copyFeedback = document.getElementById('copy-feedback');
      const cardElements = cardsGrid.querySelectorAll('.card[data-card]');

      const cardOrder = ['regulatory', 'broker', 'tax', 'stat'];
      const cardLabels = {
        regulatory: 'Regulatory Update',
        broker: 'Broker News',
        tax: 'Tax Treaty Update',
        stat: 'Stat of the Week',
      };

      function getCurrentWeekDate() {
        const now = new Date();
        const day = now.getDay();
        const monday = new Date(now);
        monday.setDate(now.getDate() - ((day + 6) % 7));
        return monday.toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' });
      }
      lastUpdatedDate.textContent = getCurrentWeekDate();

      function readCardData(cardEl) {
        const headline = cardEl.querySelector('[data-field="headline"]');
        const summary = cardEl.querySelector('[data-field="summary"]');
        const week = cardEl.querySelector('[data-field="week"]');
        return {
          headline: headline ? headline.textContent : '',
          summary: summary ? summary.textContent : '',
          week: week ? week.textContent.replace('Week of ', '') : getCurrentWeekDate(),
        };
      }

      function buildAdminForms() {
        adminCardsContainer.innerHTML = '';
        cardOrder.forEach((cardType) => {
          const cardEl = cardsGrid.querySelector(`.card[data-card="${cardType}"]`);
          if (!cardEl) return;
          const data = readCardData(cardEl);
          const div = document.createElement('div');
          div.className = 'admin-card-edit';
          div.dataset.cardType = cardType;
          div.innerHTML = `
            <label>${cardLabels[cardType]} � Headline</label>
            <input type="text" data-field="headline" value="${escapeAttr(data.headline)}">
            <label>Summary</label>
            <textarea data-field="summary">${escapeHTML(data.summary)}</textarea>
            <label>Week Date</label>
            <input type="text" data-field="week" value="${escapeAttr(data.week)}">
          `;
          adminCardsContainer.appendChild(div);
        });
      }

      function escapeAttr(str) {
        return str.replace(/&/g, '&amp;').replace(/"/g, '&quot;').replace(/</g, '&lt;').replace(/>/g, '&gt;');
      }

      function escapeHTML(str) {
        return str.replace(/&/g, '&amp;').replace(/</g, '&lt;').replace(/>/g, '&gt;');
      }

      function applyChanges() {
        const adminEdits = adminCardsContainer.querySelectorAll('.admin-card-edit');
        adminEdits.forEach((edit) => {
          const cardType = edit.dataset.cardType;
          const cardEl = cardsGrid.querySelector(`.card[data-card="${cardType}"]`);
          if (!cardEl) return;
          const headlineInput = edit.querySelector('[data-field="headline"]');
          const summaryInput = edit.querySelector('[data-field="summary"]');
          const weekInput = edit.querySelector('[data-field="week"]');
          if (headlineInput) {
            const headlineEl = cardEl.querySelector('[data-field="headline"]');
            if (headlineEl) headlineEl.textContent = headlineInput.value;
          }
          if (summaryInput) {
            const summaryEl = cardEl.querySelector('[data-field="summary"]');
            if (summaryEl) summaryEl.textContent = summaryInput.value;
          }
          if (weekInput) {
            const weekEl = cardEl.querySelector('[data-field="week"]');
            if (weekEl) weekEl.textContent = 'Week of ' + weekInput.value;
          }
        });
        lastUpdatedDate.textContent = getCurrentWeekDate();
        updateBanner.querySelector('strong').textContent = getCurrentWeekDate();
        cardElements.forEach((card) => {
          const weekEl = card.querySelector('[data-field="week"]');
          const adminEdit = adminCardsContainer.querySelector(`.admin-card-edit[data-card-type="${card.dataset.card}"]`);
          if (weekEl && adminEdit) {
            const weekInput = adminEdit.querySelector('[data-field="week"]');
            if (weekInput && weekInput.value) {
              weekEl.textContent = 'Week of ' + weekInput.value;
            }
          }
        });
      }

      function copyHTML() {
        const clone = cardsGrid.cloneNode(true);
        clone.querySelectorAll('[data-field]').forEach((el) => el.removeAttribute('data-field'));
        clone.querySelectorAll('[data-card]').forEach((el) => el.removeAttribute('data-card'));
        const html = clone.outerHTML;
        navigator.clipboard.writeText(html).then(() => {
          copyFeedback.classList.add('show');
          setTimeout(() => copyFeedback.classList.remove('show'), 2000);
        }).catch(() => {
          alert('Failed to copy. Please try again.');
        });
      }

      function toggleAdmin() {
        const isVisible = adminPanel.classList.contains('visible');
        if (isVisible) {
          adminPanel.classList.remove('visible');
        } else {
          buildAdminForms();
          adminPanel.classList.add('visible');
          adminPanel.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });
        }
      }

      document.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
        if (e.ctrlKey && e.shiftKey && e.key === 'E') {
          e.preventDefault();
          toggleAdmin();
        }
        if (e.key === 'Escape' && adminPanel.classList.contains('visible')) {
          adminPanel.classList.remove('visible');
        }
      });

      btnApply.addEventListener('click', applyChanges);
      btnCopy.addEventListener('click', copyHTML);
      btnClose.addEventListener('click', () => adminPanel.classList.remove('visible'));

      buildAdminForms();
    })();
  </script>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  :root {
    --bg-primary: #0f172a;
    --bg-secondary: #1e293b;
    --bg-card: #1a2332;
    --border: #334155;
    --text-primary: #f1f5f9;
    --text-secondary: #cbd5e1;
    --text-muted: #94a3b8;
    --accent: #D4B95A;
    --accent-hover: #d4b55a;
    --accent-bg: rgba(212, 185, 90, 0.08);
    --accent-border: rgba(212, 185, 90, 0.25);
    --red: #ef4444;
    --red-bg: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.08);
    --red-border: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
    --blue: #60a5fa;
    --blue-bg: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.08);
    --blue-border: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.2);
    --green: #22c55e;
    --green-bg: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.08);
    --green-border: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
    --purple: #a78bfa;
    --purple-bg: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.08);
    --purple-border: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.2);
    --orange: #fb923c;
    --orange-bg: rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.08);
    --orange-border: rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.2);
    --shadow-lg: 0 12px 40px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    --radius-xl: 20px;
    --radius-lg: 16px;
    --radius-md: 12px;
    --radius-sm: 8px;
  }

  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .weekly-update-container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 24px auto 0;
  }

  .header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .header .icon-circle {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent-bg);
    border: 2px solid var(--accent-border);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .header .icon-circle svg {
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .header h1 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .header h1 span {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .header p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .update-banner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: var(--accent-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-border);
    border-radius: 50px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
    width: fit-content;
    max-width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .update-banner .pulse-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    animation: pulse 1.8s ease-in-out infinite;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%,
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.35;
      transform: scale(1.7);
    }
  }

  .cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 22px 20px;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: var(--accent-border);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
  }

  .card .card-accent-bar {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
  }

  .card.regulatory .card-accent-bar { background: var(--red); }
  .card.broker .card-accent-bar { background: var(--blue); }
  .card.tax .card-accent-bar { background: var(--green); }
  .card.stat .card-accent-bar { background: var(--purple); }

  .card .category-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    width: fit-content;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .card.regulatory .category-badge {
    background: var(--red-bg);
    color: var(--red);
    border: 1px solid var(--red-border);
  }

  .card.broker .category-badge {
    background: var(--blue-bg);
    color: var(--blue);
    border: 1px solid var(--blue-border);
  }

  .card.tax .category-badge {
    background: var(--green-bg);
    color: var(--green);
    border: 1px solid var(--green-border);
  }

  .card.stat .category-badge {
    background: var(--purple-bg);
    color: var(--purple);
    border: 1px solid var(--purple-border);
  }

  .card .category-badge svg {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .card .headline {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }

  .card .summary {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
    flex: 1;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .card .date-tag {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  .card .date-tag svg {
    width: 13px;
    height: 13px;
  }

  .admin-hint {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    opacity: 0.4;
    margin-top: 8px;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .admin-panel {
    display: none;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 2px solid var(--orange);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 28px 24px;
    margin-top: 28px;
    animation: slideUp 0.35s ease;
  }

  .admin-panel.visible {
    display: block;
  }

  @keyframes slideUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(16px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .admin-panel h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--orange);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .admin-panel h2 svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
  }

  .admin-panel .admin-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .admin-card-edit {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .admin-card-edit label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .admin-card-edit input,
  .admin-card-edit textarea {
    width: 100%;
